Name: X-linked cleft palate with or without ankyloglossia
Definition: A cleft palate that has_material_basis in mutation in the TBX22 gene on chromosome Xq21.

Name: isolated cleft palate
Definition: A cleft palate seen as an isolated malformation

Name: cleft soft palate
Definition: Cleft velum is a fissure type embryopathy that affects in varying degrees the soft palate.
